13
00:01:27,746 --> 00:01:43,572
the pursuit of sensual happiness in sensual pleasures, which is low, vulgar, the way of worldlings, ignoble, unbeneficial, and the pursuit of self-mortification, which is painful, ignoble, and unbeneficial.

14
00:01:45,013 --> 00:01:55,510
Without veering towards either of these extremes, the Tathāgata has awakened to the middle way, which gives rise to vision, which gives rise to knowledge,

15
00:01:55,927 --> 00:02:00,733
and leads to peace, to direct knowledge, to enlightenment, to Nibbāna.

16
00:02:01,754 --> 00:02:05,918
And what, monks, is that middle way awakened to by the Tathāgata?

17
00:02:06,599 --> 00:02:21,176
It is this Noble Eightfold Path, that is, right view, right intention, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right concentration, and right mindfulness.

18
00:02:22,421 --> 00:02:35,056
This, monks, is that middle way, awakened to by the Tathāgata, which gives rise to vision, which gives rise to knowledge and leads to peace, to direct knowledge, to enlightenment, to Nibbāna.

19
00:02:35,075 --> 00:02:38,379
Now this, monks, is the noble truth of suffering.

20
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,381
Birth is suffering.

21
00:02:40,201 --> 00:02:41,423
Aging is suffering.

22
00:02:42,063 --> 00:02:43,324
Illness is suffering.

23
00:02:43,846 --> 00:02:46,188
Death is suffering.

24
00:02:46,209 --> 00:02:49,171
Union with what is displeasing is suffering.

25
00:02:49,860 --> 00:02:52,705
and separation from what is pleasing is suffering.

26
00:02:53,645 --> 00:02:55,968
Not to get what one wants is suffering.

27
00:02:56,530 --> 00:03:01,014
In brief, the five aggregates subject to clinging are suffering.

28
00:03:02,417 --> 00:03:05,760
Now this, monks, is the noble truth of the origin of suffering.

29
00:03:06,382 --> 00:03:15,373
It is this craving that leads to renewed existence, accompanied by delight and lust, seeking delight here and there.

30
00:03:15,873 --> 00:03:18,837
That is, craving for sensual pleasures,

31
00:03:19,358 --> 00:03:23,022
