32
00:03:24,525 --> 00:03:27,990
Now this, monks, is the noble truth of the cessation of suffering.

33
00:03:28,811 --> 00:03:40,066
It is the remainderless fading away and cessation of that same craving, the giving up and relinquishing of it, freedom from it, non-attachment.

34
00:03:41,627 --> 00:03:46,854
This, monks, is the noble truth of the way leading to the cessation of suffering.

35
00:03:46,875 --> 00:03:49,078
It is the noble Eightfold Path.

